---
title: Creamy Alfredo-Style Double Jumbo Shrimp Linguine with Bacon and Peas
description: What could be better than rich, creamy Alfredo linguine?! We've combined all the classic elements of this pasta favourite with juicy shrimp, salty bacon, spinach and bright green peas for a colourful and deliciously decadent dinner. Buon appetito!
